Create index.html page
Create a app.css file
Link index.html and app.css files
Set the text color of all <p> elements to red. Add at least 5 elements in the page.
Set the background color of the element with id="special-tag", to blue.
Set the border color of all elements with the class="group", to green.
In index.html add 2 parent elements:
top-parent
bottom-parrent
In each parent element add 3 div elements.
For each div element from top-parent set the following CSS properties:
dotted border
thickness = 4px
color = orange
width = 10em
height = 50px
For each div element from bottom-parent set the following CSS properties:
dashed border
thickness = 2px
color = violet
width = 100px
height = 4rem
